TECH STACK REFERENCE (docs/TECH_STACK.md)
==============================================================================

Tech Stack: Rust monorepo with axum, tokio, sqlx (PostgreSQL), tracing, tower/tower-http.
- Control plane: Rust (axum, tokio, sqlx), REST + SSE, PostgreSQL
- Workers: Rust (tokio, reqwest, git2); agent via Claude Code or Cursor CLI (BYOL)
- CLI: Rust (clap), SSE for tail and attach, shares api-types with server
- Web UI: React + TypeScript, Vite, TanStack Query, SSE
- Logging: JSON; dual-write (local files + central DB); SSE for tail
- Auth: API key (CLI, Web, workers); TLS for all connections

Repo layout:
remote_harness/
├── crates/
│   ├── server/              # Control plane (axum, API, engine, sessions, logs)
│   ├── worker/              # Worker (reqwest, git2, runs Claude Code / Cursor CLI)
│   ├── cli/                 # CLI (clap, API client, log tail)
│   └── api-types/           # Shared: request/response types, IDs, contracts (serde)
├── web/                     # Web UI (Vite + React)
├── Cargo.toml               # Workspace root
├── docker-compose.yml
└── README.md

